the river why is a 2010 american independent drama film directed by matthew leutwyler .   it is an adaptation of the 1983 sierra club novel of the same name by david james duncan and stars zach gilford , william hurt and amber heard .   showtime broadcast the film in august 2011 and was later screened in the united states as benefit for fish and river conservation groups .   the film was released on blu-ray and dvd on november 8 , 2011 .   the film won the award for best cinematography at the ashland film festival and the audience award for best film at the naples international film festival .   the film 's title is a homophone of the river wye .